\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n移民金門真係諗得過 黎緊會開家樂福(類似Walmart 大超市) 生活機能將大大提升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ef595c3eaf0bd0a329935557143c39181eeb6a","tid":223410,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>移民金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n移民金門真係諗得過 黎緊會開家樂福(類似Walmart 大超市) 生活機能將大大提升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價如何 金門聽講無咩工商業活動"},{"pid":"58054ba14d88b15b76e5d53b2cfb88323124ee28","tid":223410,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>移民金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n移民金門真係諗得過 黎緊會開家樂福(類似Walmart 大超市) 生活機能將大大提升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價如何 金門聽講無咩工商業活動</blockquote><br />\n最殘酷部分 樓價拍得住新北市 <br />\n每個老人手上都有幾棟獨立屋，幾塊農田，完勝80%香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021336dce1f3308e4412c5cb68af4725a48b5601","tid":223410,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>移民金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n移民金門真係諗得過 黎緊會開家樂福(類似Walmart 大超市) 生活機能將大大提升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價如何 金門聽講無咩工商業活動</blockquote><br />\n工商業活動係有限，但係唔代表完全死城，其實都有兩三個小市區，基本的台式食品、奶茶都有得飲，台妹都有得睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47e990a16e224e94f805840589094b49fc11429","tid":223410,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戰地風光呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nup 唔到圖住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 晏少少"},{"pid":"afa4181527dcadb45fbac9c86b93b07ab795d45b","tid":223410,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留定名睇遊記</blockquote><br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0312c6f361669e1780b9677d42f1363fa1be97","tid":223410,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>移民金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n移民金門真係諗得過 黎緊會開家樂福(類似Walmart 大超市) 生活機能將大大提升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價如何 金門聽講無咩工商業活動</blockquote><br />\n最殘酷部分 樓價拍得住新北市 <br />\n每個老人手上都有幾棟獨立屋，幾塊農田，完勝80%香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁去黎做咩 完全唔吸引<br />\n台灣島大把地方選擇點解要選擇金門"},{"pid":"cfbd2a05ff1cf86375ec2e634a926a0f3785bba8","tid":223410,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>移民金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n移民金門真係諗得過 黎緊會開家樂福(類似Walmart 大超市) 生活機能將大大提升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓價如何 金門聽講無咩工商業活動</blockquote><br />\n最殘酷部分 樓價拍得住新北市 <br />\n每個老人手上都有幾棟獨立屋，幾塊農田，完勝80%香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁去黎做咩 完全唔吸引<br />\n台灣島大把地方選擇點解要選擇金門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整體黎講，台灣本島發展變慢，金門前景被看好，尤其係觀光業。<br />\n<br />\n環境而言，台灣本島生活緊張，居住環境較逼，污染較嚴重。金門污染較少，生活節奏慢，但係金門人工會比本島高(有離島津貼)，基本上係儲錢好地方。<br />\n<br />\n金門空氣清新，而且近大陸，方便係大陸做生意的台灣/大陸人。"},{"pid":"078923fdde70d7e89ea122848ccb6b713c3d748b","tid":223410,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"認真PO無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610dbb4012fe87b2bcb304161ba6b61ae6719988","tid":223410,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"想去玩人妻"},{"pid":"b1c56d86419ab7c05327691b890c76655a40805b","tid":223410,"uid":104217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"留明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc58a106f596ed414e178c534f8c8c66d28a212","tid":223410,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"btw 問下， 台北 台中 台南 邊度會受地震打風威脅大啲？"},{"pid":"7a5f93414cff14beadc20ffa9a957f17214b05e6","tid":223410,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"金門離大陸咁近"}]}